Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.63,0:01:34.06,Top,,0,0,0,,Dear, I brought tea.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.81,Top,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's that letter...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.53,0:01:37.82,Top,,0,0,0,,No, I was just...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.82,0:01:44.17,Top,,0,0,0,,Really, dear, how many times do you need to read that letter from Isabel and Pat to feel satisfied?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.27,0:01:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fault all they do is make us worry. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe those mischievous twins.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Making lots of friends is great,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.45,0:01:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but all they ever write about is fun stuff—\Nlike going to the circus or how cute that puppy is. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.89,0:02:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a word about what actually matters—studying!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.42,0:02:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, are they really paying enough attention to studying? I'm worried too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.69,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They say exams are around the corner.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we need to give them a little scare.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.20,0:02:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A scare?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.44,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Without that, they might even end up \Nyawning openly during class.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how we solve it...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.39,0:02:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? {wakarimashita ne = do you understand? - "ne" is a weak suggesting ending particle, as in "you do understand, don't you"}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You must keep this formula in mind at all times.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand? {wakarimashita ka = do you understand? - ka is a stronger, interrogative ending particle, as in "you do understand, DO you?" - this needs to be worded differently from 2:37}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.38,0:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.93,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that true, Miss Roberts?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This formula?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.54,0:02:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone snapped out of it so suddenly... {lit: sharply opened their eyes}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This formula will be on the exam.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.75,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts said her usual keyword. {lit: miss robert's usual habit}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.41,0:03:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When she says "Do you understand?"
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a given! {/100% guarantee [it'll be in the exam]}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your exams are finally coming up next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you'll have to start taking it seriously, no slacking. {lit: you'll have to tighten your frivolous feelings}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A total of nine subjects.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do study in earnest so you won’t regret it later.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today's class.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no fun... {depression; melancholy; dejection; gloom; despondency}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.09,0:03:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first exam after coming to St. Clare's, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not confident at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.36,0:03:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Clare's education is on a whole other level.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.53,0:03:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just keeping up with the form \Ntook all my strength this term.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.31,0:04:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be you, Binks. \NNo exams, no worries.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Knew I would find you here. \NYou've got a letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Pat, it's from Dad!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,From Dad?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.63,0:04:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Isabel, Pat, your exams \Nare around the corner, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.10,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you two gave me your word \Nbefore leaving for St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.46,0:04:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,'Since we've always been #1 and #2 \Nback at Redroofs, at a school such as St. Clare's...'" {https://grammarist.com/punctuation/how-to-quote-within-quote/}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What about a school such as ours?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, you can't!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't read it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.46,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.46,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.99,0:04:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"At a school such as St. Clare's, \Nwhere their level of education is so low,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.23,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we both swear to be the very best \Nin every subject."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.17,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Did you really say that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't really mean it. {lit: we reflected on it now/took it back}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.61,0:05:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"I believe that my daughters \Naren't the kind to break their promises.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad." {actually "datte" = like that/that's all}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.41,0:05:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.85,0:05:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what comes of having \Ntoo much faith in yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, let's prepare.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you? \NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.90,0:05:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling home.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that much...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Is that you, Mum?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My, Isabel? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna keep our vows!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.78,0:05:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not in every subject, but we’ll get the top marks in the school on this exam! {lit: become #1 [among all students]}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.10,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.75,0:05:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see! {/definitely}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.39,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.65,0:05:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea, Isabel?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.53,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to please Dad and Mum.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.83,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.54,0:06:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was being selfish, saying things like
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.14,0:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't want to go to St. Clare's, \Nadults are the worst," and all that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.21,0:06:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is, both Mum and Dad \Nreally do care about me and you wholeheartedly,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.98,0:06:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,so I want to show them how grateful I am, \Nget good grades on these exams,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.18,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and show them how much I care!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But with our current {academic }abilities...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.96,0:06:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, just imagine it for a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.93,0:06:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How happy do you think Mum and Dad \Nwill be if we get the top marks?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum will probably...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! She’ll put on a feast.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A huge party as if it were both a birthday \Nand Christmas at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.98,0:06:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And as for Dad...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He never praised us in front of others... {?????? lit: before the two, never praise - maybe "he never praised us two before" but that'd be very weird; those two are probably the lawyer and the aunt they're talking about next, but i've no clue why they attach such great significance to being praised before two random people}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.32,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the lawyer Mr. Edgar... {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.98,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and Aunt Morley come...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll brag about us! {iifurasu = to spread (e.g. a rumor); to circulate; to disseminate}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.95,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"My word, it turns out my naughty twins \Ncan be quite capable too!"
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{the sound of emitting the pipe smoke}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.16,0:07:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! And then he'll go like...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit embarrassed, though... {???????? only hear hazukashii}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.17,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then, Isabel.\NIf we work together, there's nothing we can't do!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Pat! Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... I'll blast through it! {lit; I'm on fire}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get them top grades!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.42,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our number one rival is Hilary.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.00,0:07:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There hasn’t been a single year when she didn’t come out on top in the maths and French exams.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there's Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Second place is informally reserved for Joan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But in natural sciences, \Nshe's even better than Hilary. {rika = science (inc. mathematics, medicine, etc.); natural science​}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.36,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to stay sharp.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Janet an unlikely contender? {?? ooana is probably "long-shot win (in horse racing, etc.); big winnings (on a long shot); a killing (made from a bet)" - w/e that means}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kathleen also seems to be serious about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.50,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's Sheila who's the expert in classic literature. {??? koten = classic (work, esp. book); the classics (probably)}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh… so the whole form are our rivals? {sounds odd but is apparently acceptable in British English}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That just means we too...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,must fight back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.99,0:08:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,French Revolution, \Nin the Gregorian calendar.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,1789.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And who was the king at the time?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.87,0:08:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Binks!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You decided to study with us?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.58,0:08:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered! Louis XVI.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.09,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{and...}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleepy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{mo? dunno, maybe "Dammit..." or "No..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who're you calling sleepy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's strive on for ten more minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, twenty minutes!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, your exams finally start today.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.33,0:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe all of you \Nhave been preparing earnestly.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, \Nwe've done everything we could.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.19,0:09:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{yeah}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, everyone,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,please begin.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.14,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How was it, Pat?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.16,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A total flop. \NI got stuck on the very first maths problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.35,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent so long wrestling with it \NI got nothing on everything else.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And my French prep completely misfired. {yama ga hazureru - a test preparation slang, when you only focus on one part of the course, neglecting everything else and expecting it to be in the exam, but you guess it completely wrong}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.55,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Why do I always get questions \Nthat I haven't prepared for?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They say they'll announce today's results \Ntomorrow morning already.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... God help me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday's test results have been posted!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... What am I gonna do? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Incredible! Hilary is number one again!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.49,0:10:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.01,0:10:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in maths and French!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! That's our Hilary!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Congrats, Hilary.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.45,0:10:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Joan. You're first \Nin natural sciences yourself. Congrats!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.52,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, just as you'd expect...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We might still be number two...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, did I really lose to the twins?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where? Where are we?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There, in maths.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.56,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm number 13, and Isabel...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.01,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 9...!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 12 for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.83,0:10:39.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,The exams went by in a flash, and before we knew it, \Neight of the subjects were over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Grandma? Hear this!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.11,0:10:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was number two in natural sciences!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you cheered me on.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.18,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A trip to Scotland as a reward? \NWait, seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were number three \Nin classic literature and grammar?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.89,0:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And I can't wait to tell \Nmy Dad and Mum about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.32,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also number two in history.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.44,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So the best we ever got in the eight subjects was Isabel’s fifth in classical literature?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I fell flat completely.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.73,0:11:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All that remains is geography tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our last chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's focus all your strength on geography, \Nand you’ll ace it tomorrow. {???? lit: write tomorrow}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.36,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's go to the study \Nand review my notes again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've arranged them so neatly!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there’ll be questions \Non Africa’s climate and produce.{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Let's recheck everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.02,0:11:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The names of towns and harbours too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.72,0:11:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as perfect as it gets.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My head feels like it weighs a ton.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still knitting that sweater? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, little by little.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.52,0:12:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, my knitting book is...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in the classroom?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.33,0:12:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.07,0:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I just can't bring myself to remember \Nthe names of rivers in Africa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I know! Let's go and write them on your desk in the classroom now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.61,0:12:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you cheating now, Janet?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.88,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Miss Roberts never allows anyone \Nto enter the classroom during exam week.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.52,0:12:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's because the test questions \Nare in the classroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.72,0:12:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is at St. Clare's.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,What should we do? \NIsabel is there right now... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey everybody! \NHilary is handing out cookies.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Cookies?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.77,0:12:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Pat?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They look heavenly delicious!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's chocolate cookies with roses. {lit: decorated with roses - unlikely that it's cream roses since it's cookies and not cakes so idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,Isabel will be back \Nas soon as she gets her knitting book.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't come now, \Nthere'll be none left for you! {lit: pat's share will be taken too}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, it's pitch black! \NOh, crumbs! {?? yaba is probably "oh no [I can't find my book in this darkness]"; oh crumbs is their typical interjection in the book}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's geography questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be stupid. \NWhat are you thinking, Isabel?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.89,0:13:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.00,0:13:59.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,What am I doing? I know full well \NI mustn't look at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.31,0:14:05.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,How happy do you think Mum and Dad \Nwill be if we get the top marks?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.98,0:14:10.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,Mum will probably... \NI know! She’ll put on a feast.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.15,0:14:13.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,A huge party as if it were both a birthday \Nand Christmas at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.07,0:14:18.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,They're questions on Africa, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,And what I've just studied.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,This too?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,This too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Took you long enough. \NHuh? Where's your knitting book?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... M-My knitting book...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.25,0:14:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I found it. It's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.06,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, I'm going to bed now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.46,0:14:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? \NYou're strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.77,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you, Pat. \NDon't ask anything. Just don't!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, \Nwe'll get through it together, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.86,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't forgive me if I told you, I know... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel, d-did you...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.75,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The test questions were there,\Non the teacher's desk.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.49,0:15:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've seen them all!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's gotten into me, \NI've lost control. {lit: my head became crazy, I became obsessed}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.43,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be! \NYou'd never do something so...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.17,0:15:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe that!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the O'Sullivan twins, \Naren't about all that sly stuff! {lit: don't do cowardly things}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we took pride in.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.61,0:15:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If what you say is true...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.71,0:16:06.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,Pat is right. I'm a cheat. {lit: cowardly person}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I take first place by peeking at the questions,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.80,0:16:13.81,Thought,,0,0,0,,nobody will be proud of me—\Nleast of all Dad and Mum!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm such a fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.64,0:16:56.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,If I were Isabel, I would've done \Nthe same thing for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,So how can I... {???? /and yet, I...}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Isabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know. {what you're going to say}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna withdraw from the exam, right? {/you won't be taking the exam}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.72,0:17:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Confess everything to Miss Roberts.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.16,0:17:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see right through you! \NThat's what I'd do if I were Isabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel, I just wanna say...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.83,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to withdraw \Nfrom the exam too, Pat? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To share my plight with me, right? {??? lit: because you don't want me alone to endure sad thoughts}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But how... {??? assuming [did you know]}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.87,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell. That's what I would've done if I were you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.94,0:18:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're twins, remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.24,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you take that exam, for both of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.39,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.69,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally taking \Nyour last exam today—geography.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you are satisfied \Nwith the marks you’ve got,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.80,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,some regret not working harder,\N but either way, you’ve one more subject to face. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hand out the question sheets now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.81,0:18:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.81,0:18:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I must confess something to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Isabel?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll accept any punishment you deem fit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.89,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, last night...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.75,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the wrong questions here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for the second form.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.28,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the first form.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.34,0:19:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The questions for the first form \Nare probably in the second form classroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.94,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilary, would you please go and swap them?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.72,0:19:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The questions you saw \Nwere for the second form.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't meant for us!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it you wanted to confess?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right... It's that...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.58,0:19:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Um… last night, we both munched \Non some cookies when we were already in bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... That's what it was, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.54,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.88,0:19:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do with you children...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.00,0:19:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now {\i1}these{\i0} are your actual questions.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everyone get a sheet?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.96,0:19:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.42,0:19:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get started, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.59,0:19:54.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,They're questions on Africa!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,But they're completely different \Nfrom what I saw.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.36,0:20:02.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,It's just the stuff me and Isabel studied last night. \NI might just be able to pull it off!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.48,0:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The exams are over, at last.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.25,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this strange tremor in my hands,\NI probably got it all wrong. {lit: didn't write good answers}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's fine too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.12,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Strangely enough, \NI feel completely refreshed.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{yeah}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.36,0:20:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even matter that I'm not the number one, \NI feel so relieved now!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez Louise, who's that belching here? {lit: ara ara, you produced loud voice}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The geography results are out.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's number one? \NHilary? Joan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One-two...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Patricia O'Sullivan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the number one!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.12,0:20:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.52,0:20:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of reaction is that, Pat?\NWe just said you've got first place.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.93,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Pat!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isabel, we earned that first place together.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.64,0:21:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dad, Mum, we’ve done it at last—\Nthe coveted first place!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.51,0:21:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only number six, \Nbut I have no regrets!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.72,0:21:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no other exam has ever made me understand so deeply both the pain and the joy of studying!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.99,0:21:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have been number one time after time \Nin many subjects at our old school,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.76,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but now I realise—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.03,0:21:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ending up in sixth place after worrying, \Npondering, and giving it my all
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.14,0:21:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is worth far more than winning a first place \Nyou can't help but take for granted!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, Mum...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.58,0:21:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wish I could've gotten even better results \Nto make you even happier.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.95,0:21:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the feeling I want to convey right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the next exam, for sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.69,0:22:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're wonderful kids, \Nthe kind we can be proud of.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.63,0:22:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Our two mischievous treasures.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.90,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes.}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.25,0:23:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The long-awaited school concert \Nis almost upon us.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.78,0:23:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I memorised Romeo’s \Nlong speeches to perfection.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.32,0:23:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone just waits for the actual show.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.12,0:23:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, with the school concert being less than a day away...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.66,0:23:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrible incident happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.26,0:23:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Vera, who plays Juliet, \Nfell off the set and hurt her leg!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.40,0:23:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to suddenly give the role of Juliet to someone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.23,0:23:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Just as everything \Nwas coming along so nicely...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.85,0:23:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twins at St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.57,0:24:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Disaster! Who Will Take the Role?" {大ピンチ! 代役は誰に}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.39,0:24:03.89,Note,,0,0,0,,Episode 12 \NA Disaster! Who Will Take the Role? {大ピンチ! 代役は誰に}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.91,0:24:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
